Developer Terms of Use
des:
Wize Talk Radio a listener-supported, 24-hour non-commercial, non-political Internet Gospel radio station.
We are committed to making your radio experience on the Internet the best. You can help us accomplish our goals with your heart felt feedback, your support, and by telling others about us.

Our Programming includes, interviews, bible study, spirited discussions on current issues. We offer diversified genres of Gospel music including but not limited to: Hip-Hop/Praise/Worship Music/Jazz/Rap/Blues/ Southern Gospel/ Country/Inspirational and Reggae.

Our Target Audience

Our aspiration is to reach:

Christians and non-Christians, those who are committed to a faith and those who are not apart of the church community.
People who have lost a desire for the things of God and those who never had a desire for God.
People who believe in God and are like-minded to Christian values.
People who don’t go to church but want to find spiritual meaning for life.
